James Lesure https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/James_Lesure 0 James Lesure (born September 21, 1970) is an American television actor, best known for roles on the NBC/The WB sitcom For Your Love (1998-2002), and NBC comedy-drama Las Vegas (2003-2008).
